name: sacrifice and reward part 2
description:
Animated oil painting in mp4 video to run in loop 

"the time that passed was enough for me to forget, honestly forget that I wanted what I wanted so much that I sacrificed my entire being, everything I believe... In time of time, it must have been a few hours actually,
when the sounds of tired wings echoed on the porch of the house, and there he was, surrendered to me, as my will said. 
I confess that I could only think that I was ready to destroy all my reality again..." 

Meow ><
